dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially.   Inset map of Fish Bay, Disko Island and coast of Greenland.   The fourth state of a map originally published by Frederik de Wit in 1675.   From: Atlas van zeevaart en koophandel door de geheele weereldt ... / ... door den Heer Louis Renard ... Te Amsterdam : by Reinier en Iosua Ottens, 1745. Dimensions: 48 x 54 centimeters
